---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Seasonal Pottery Painting"
  description="Paint seasonal designs for holidays and celebrations in Centerville, TN. Perfect for every season!"
  price="$15-25"
  duration="1-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="seasonal pottery, holiday pottery painting, seasonal decorations, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Seasonal Pottery Painting - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Celebrate every season with custom-painted pottery pieces at Made @ The Local Pottery and Candle Studio. Our Seasonal Pottery Painting experience lets you create holiday and seasonal decorations that are uniquely yours.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Design and paint pottery pieces with seasonal themes—spring flowers, summer beach scenes, autumn leaves, winter snowflakes, or holiday motifs. Whether it's Easter eggs, Valentine's Day decorations, Halloween pumpkins, Thanksgiving pieces, or Christmas ornaments, we have seasonal pottery collections and design inspiration. Paint with colors and styles that match your home's seasonal décor. After you finish, we professionally glaze and kiln-fire your pieces so they're durable and beautiful for years of seasonal display.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Seasonal pottery piece selection</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints</li>
      <li>Seasonal design inspiration and guidance</li>
      <li>Quality brushes and supplies</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Take home your seasonal decoration</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Holiday and seasonal decorating</li>
      <li>Creating unique holiday gifts</li>
      <li>Building seasonal decoration collections</li>
      <li>Home décor that changes with seasons</li>
      <li>Family seasonal activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your seasonal piece (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Choose seasonal design themes (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your seasonal design (45-60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final details and glazing (10 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $15-25<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Paint your seasonal pottery!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Paint seasonal pieces every few months! My home looks decorated and personal. Love this tradition!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Diane M.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made custom Halloween decorations! They're way better than store-bought and so much more special!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Kevin P.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Our Christmas pottery pieces are family heirlooms now! Paint new ones every year. Love this!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>The Wilson Family</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Holiday Ornament Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Create custom holiday ornaments for your tree.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/holiday-ornament-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint Your Own Pottery Session</h3>
        <p>Choose from pre-made pottery pieces and paint them your way.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/paint-your-own-pottery-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Ceramic Painting Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional ceramic painting techniques in our structured workshop.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/ceramic-painting-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
